{"tid":1693522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"收到個電話講普通話叫我區選記得去投票","createTime":"2019-11-04T15:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T12:27:07.000Z","uid":116342,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"78390685315a3e4ab28ea8d87056a93fd70ddd38","tid":1693522,"uid":116342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"今日朝早收到個電話講普通話叫我區選記得去投票，個號碼重要上星期先係中國移動申請(sor 工作需要)。<br />\n<br />\n電話:63756625<br />\n<br />\n問佢點解有我電話，佢話我入左個組織，普通話太差聽唔清楚。朋友話佢無講要我投邊個，無違反選舉守則，但係要知己知彼，證明在大陸人開始運用大陸票搞區選。<br />\n<br />\n有無人都收到？<br />\n<br />\n如果黎緊幾日收到，麻煩問到個組織名<br />\n<br />\n各位小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a001839c068b122e902c365abb47586f8b77cd","tid":1693522,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"應該係你呢個電話號碼嘅上手入咗會"},{"pid":"f00ffb801bd75f61958cb94df7db5e0323741d33","tid":1693522,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1a001839c068b122e902c365abb47586f8b77cd","tid":1693522,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"應該係你呢個電話號碼嘅上手入咗會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:22:33.000Z","msg":"中移動"},{"pid":"5c0b8c466dbb00a0cbf6fc7ceec30211ab566ac8","tid":1693522,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"支那移動&hellip;&hellip;謎底已經解開"},{"pid":"492a8d30b6cec4f69b9457b482ecfa6902f39494","tid":1693522,"uid":116342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c0b8c466dbb00a0cbf6fc7ceec30211ab566ac8","tid":1693522,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"支那移動&hellip;&hellip;謎底已經解開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"我都知用佢服務係柒左，但係如果再有人收到呢個組織既電話，就可以知道對方係邊個"}]}